These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
House: art-deco, cape-cod, townhouse, cottage
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, egyptian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: rat, dog, snake, hedgehog
 1. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
 2. the cottage house is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the canadian##8
 4. the owner of the rat is not the cottage house##6
 5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the egyptian##1
 7. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
 8. the cape-cod house is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
 9. the art-deco house is not the turkish##6
10. the owner of the dog is the turkish##1
11. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
12. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
13. the cottage house is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
14. the egyptian is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| House    | art-deco         | cottage     | townhouse     | cape-cod         |
| Nationality   | german | turkish    | egyptian     | canadian |
| Pet   | rat       | dog | hedgehog | snake       |

