.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
City: edinburgh, liverpool, paris, colone
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, marigold, sunflower
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, ebony, light-blue, grey
 1. the person who growsmarigold is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the person who growsrose is not the person traveling to paris##6
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| City   | paris          | edinburgh      | colone      | liverpool   |
| Flower        | marigold     | rose | begonia | sunflower      |
| Color      | grey | ebony    | blue  | light-blue |

