There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, aquamarine, orange, ebony
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, milk, lemonade
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 5. the person drinking water is not the person who likes amber##6
 6. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person who likes amber is not to the right of the person who likes ebony##8
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4
10. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | satire  | martial-arts | scientific | disaster |
| Color   | aquamarine  | amber      | ebony | orange        |
| Beverage     | water | milk       | lemonade    | 7up     |

