 7. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
 8. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the victorian house is the person who likes turquise##1
