.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, fish, snake, goldfish
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, librarian, scientist, musician
There 4 different types of food: spinach, peach, blueberry, cucumber
 1. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the social-worker##1
 3. the social-worker is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
 5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the musician##1
 6. the musician is not the owner of the snake##6
 7. the owner of the pony is not the person eating blueberry##6
 8. the librarian is the person eating blueberry##1
 9. the scientist is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
10. the person eating cucumber is the owner of the snake##1
11. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the scientist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | snake       | pony | fish  | goldfish    |
| Job   | scientist       | musician    | librarian | social-worker    |
| Food         | cucumber | spinach   | blueberry   | peach |

