The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, scooter, motorbike
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, videographer, mechanic, software-developer
 1. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 2. the person driving the motorbike is not the videographer##6
 3. the mechanic is somewhere between the person who likes purple and the person driving the motorbike##7
 4. the videographer is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 5. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 6. the mechanic is the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 8. the software-developer is between the person who likes pink and the mechanic##2
 9. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person who likes pink##8
10. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person who likes apricot##8
11. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Color          | purple      | grey      | apricot | pink |
| Transport   | scooter | ship    | motorbike | quad-bike     |
| Job   | doctor    | mechanic | software-developer  | videographer |

