.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-7::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, apricot, peas
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, poker, scrabble
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, august, december
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 2. the person playing bridge is not the person eating peas##6
 3. the person playing bridge is between the person playing poker and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person playing scrabble##6
 8. the person eating apricot is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
 9. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
10. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
11. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
12. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
13. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Food   | peach   | broccoli | peas        | apricot |
| Game   | poker | bridge   | billiard | scrabble     |
| Birthday     | december      | april      | august      | october        |

