.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, backgammon, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, documentary, scientific, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, r&b, gospel
 1. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
 2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person watching scientific movies##7
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
 4. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 8. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
10. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
11. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
13. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
14. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Game         | go    | backgammon | monopoly | mah-jongg    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | romance    | action      | documentary |
| Music-Genre     | reggae | dubstep          | gospel      | r&b       |

