.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, manager, dressmaker, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, house, blues, disco
House: cottage, craftsman, wooden, farmhouse
1. the fan of d&b is the cottage house##1
2. the manager is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
3. the farmhouse house is between the fan of d&b and the fan of disco##2
4. the social-worker is on the right of the fan of house##1
5. the manager is not the wooden house##6
6. the fan of disco is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the wooden house is somewhere between the farmhouse house and the craftsman house##7
8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
